
Given	I'm logged-in with valid credentials
And Age is <18 years
And	I go to Page 04 of Elbow MRI

When I select 'Finding' radio button
Then 'Finding' dropdown menu is enabled

When I select 'Bone Marrow Edema' from the dropdown menu
Then 'Add new finding' button is enabled
And 'Humerus, lateral epicondyle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Humerus, medial epicondyle' checkbox is enabled
And 'Radial head' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ulna, proximal' checkbox is enabled
And 'Olecranon' checkbox is enabled

And 'Subchondral' radio button is enabled
And 'Focal' radio button is enabled
And 'Diffuse' radio button is enabled

And 'Subchondral fracture' checkbox is enabled
And 'Impaction' checkbox is enabled
And 'Epicondylitis humeri' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Humerus, medial epicondyle' checkbox
Then 'Apophysitis' checkbox is enabled

When I select 'Epicondylitis humeri' checkbox
Then 'Radial' checkbox is enabled
And 'Ulnar' checkbox is enabled
